        <labelNoun>a quantum rush</labelNoun>
        <description>The extreme stimulant effects of Nuka-Cola Quantum. Massive boost to all capabilities, but at a cost.</description>
        <hediffClass>Hediff_High</hediffClass>
        <defaultLabelColor>(0.4,0.7,1)</defaultLabelColor>
